== Nudge distance ==

The nudge distance is displayed in the BIM status bar at the bottom of the FreeCAD window. You can:

* Click the nudge value to change it manually
* Set it to '''auto''' to automatically scale based on zoom level
* Enter a specific value in the current unit system

In auto mode, the nudge distance adapts to the view:
* Zoomed out = larger nudge steps
* Zoomed in = smaller nudge steps

== Usage ==

# Select one or more objects in the [[3D_view|3D View]].
# Use any of the nudge keyboard shortcuts listed above.
# The selected objects move by the configured nudge distance.

